{"tid":1447824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民武裝呢個係唯一方法","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T23:49:07.000Z","uid":77267,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c6c7561d94ffa2d6174e5109c9e4c76a6f753c","tid":1447824,"uid":77267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:02.000Z","msg":"今日係最黑暗既一日，見到一米開槍，㩒住係地下講哂投降都繼續㩒，女義士爆眼同面骨，地鐵站射煙，飛虎扮示威者，我想講一唔以黎你地爭取過啲咩？我見到出面有post叫勇武停一停我同意，但等大家休息完要做既野唔該係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全民武裝</span></span>，唔好再講咩野接收工，唔係話佢阻唔阻嚇到啲狗，而係你覺得咁樣可以收尾?<br />\n<br />\n係呢一刻唔好再有教條主義，唔好再對前線玩火做咩野行為去割蓆，唔好再妄想係極權政府手上唔流血抗爭去贏，你要絕食和理非佔路可以繼續做唔割，但我希望你諗下仲想犧牲幾多手足坐監，永久損害，以死去喚醒大家。<br />\n<br />\n2個月啦，你想爭取咩野?你見到成班手足咁樣你可以做到咩野程度，你為左個6位義士同盲同坐監既手足你肯唔肯捉緊你既拳頭，唔好講咩野長期抗爭，sorry呀你地無本錢，有你都係拎緊手足既生命去玩，睇下班狗追你地拋棄隊友既樣?可恥?返到屋企睇返條片係咩感受呀？<br />\n<br />\n當你地醒覺哂唔該做好文宣全民抗命，就算真子彈我都唔怕同你企出黎，收埋你今日既憤怒，等待時機，呢一場係革命，唔好再怕，因為你冇得再輸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"eebe0a8b28017304b9835d33d06a692e97882b17","tid":1447824,"uid":77267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民武裝文宣</span></span>"},{"pid":"7e19bc7e2551570acec3073eeb926bd21f7fea94","tid":1447824,"uid":77267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民武裝無得再輸啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"4fd0db5d40559e4b641d54490d88c152f4c7b7fc","tid":1447824,"uid":77267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民武裝</span></span>"},{"pid":"131aaafd1358bb22eaa9c5951bf3d10b4e844e45","tid":1447824,"uid":77267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民武裝</span></span>"},{"pid":"0f2b24a70c86935a4fe2fe30463f8d23d37591cb","tid":1447824,"uid":77267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:09.000Z","msg":"你地仲想去機場煲大啲咩，煲大完又可以點，等其他國家救我地?2個月啦"},{"pid":"b381a30f539cc72b243b7bc90605d36f7e7e2c2c","tid":1447824,"uid":77267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民武裝</span></span>"},{"pid":"2f3d3f079ed4b3509589c5a8c8154e76f5217824","tid":1447824,"uid":77267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6oFObe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6oFObe.png&h=56f39cef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e15a5f74067577ec1acbad78d83baf6a680ded5c","tid":1447824,"uid":77267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民武裝</span>"},{"pid":"fa4507127da638b08ffd28e2fc296755a2fb9780","tid":1447824,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"而家個個成身防具，冇武器<br />\n有冇人會整個list講吓攻擊性武器？"},{"pid":"c1f4918ba706e42c2e668fd147f09107a0cef2b3","tid":1447824,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:48.000Z","msg":"要升級  一定要搞攻擊性武器<br />\n班黑警已經完全喪失人性  成班都陷家鏟"},{"pid":"e710f242b3f2aefc5463014f070d3420e60fc090","tid":1447824,"uid":119055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:35.000Z","msg":"cant agree more<br />\n黑警還眼!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"551b38b2aa23a34aaad4c0a9951e9c15e9290b42","tid":1447824,"uid":77267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa4507127da638b08ffd28e2fc296755a2fb9780","tid":1447824,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"而家個個成身防具，冇武器<br />\n有冇人會整個list講吓攻擊性武器？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0